          _
 ___  ___| | ___      selo is a Konpu subproject
/ __|/ _ \ |/ _ \     that creates fonts from the
\__ \  __/ | (_) |   glyphs available in ilo Konpu
|___/\___|_|\___/     ___________________________
                        _  __
      ____       ___   | |/ /___ _ _  _ __ _  _
     ||  || |   |_|_|  | ' </ _ \ ' \| '_ \ || |
     ||  || |___  |    |_|\_\___/_||_| .__/\_,_|
                                     |_|

Makefile     Makefile to creating files in font.out/
scripts/     Scripts: utilities and scripts to output a .selo file
fonts.in/    C Preprocessor rules building parts of .selo fonts
fonts.out/   Generated Fonts:

               - .selo : generated font consisting of lines:
                         <UTF-codepoint> <Description of a Konpu Glyph>
                         Can be previewed with selo-view script

               - .flf  : FIGlet fonts generated from the .selo font
                         Can be used with FIGlet (and selo-figlet wrapper)

               - .kbitx: Bits'n'Picas file generated from the .selo font
